* Sublime was about to get involved with this bunch of Maximals when 
movement suddenly caught her eye and she looked towards the three Autobots 
that just came around.
< More people to meet!>
* After they were done talking she quietly walked over to them, though 
didn't know exactly what to do.*

" Um..." *she bit her lip in thought for a sec.*

" Hello. I'm Sublime. Who are you guys?"

* The first bot she held her hand out to was Cliffjumper.*
